description[0]_en: A gathering or organization of persons bearing a particular name and capable of acting as a unit.

description[0]_en: A designation that refers to an RDA entity.

description[0]_en: An abstract class of key conceptual objects in the universe of human discourse that is a focus of interest to users of RDA metadata in a system for resource discovery.
note[0]_en: An RDA entity includes an agent, collective agent, corporate body, expression, family, item, manifestation, nomen, person, place, timespan, and work.
